item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossy)】M4A - Miley Cyrus - Endless Summer Vacation (Acoustic)
item.description:
Here's a completely stripped down version of the entire album i've been putting together for a while. I got the idea from some YouTube channels (which are credited below). I used the Dolby Atmos files and some Al websites to extract the vocals, I tried to make them as clear as possible and I used some "hidden" vocals too. I also used some background vocals from the Backyard Sessions to compensate what I couldn't salvage from the studio version. I hope you enjoy it!

TRACKLIST:

Flowers (Acoustic)
Jaded (Acoustic)
Rose Colored Lenses (Acoustic)
Used To Be Young (Acoustic)
Thousand Miles (Acoustic)
You (Acoustic)
Handstand (Acoustic)
River (Acoustic)
Violet Chemistry (Acoustic)
Muddy Feet (feat. Sia) [Acoustic]
Wildcard (Acoustic)
Island (Acoustic)
Wonder Woman (Acoustic)

CREDITS:

Tracks 1-3,5,6,8 & 10-13 YT: sing2guitar
Track 4 YT: iplayandyousing9496
Tracks 7 & 9 YT: KhaToGuitar95 ​
